# Earlybird PingPong App

## Setup

Update the following files with your mnemonic phrase where it says `<ADD YOUR MNEMONIC HERE>`

1. `/script/sendPingOnRukhPingPoingApp.sh`
2. `/script/sendPingOnThunderbirdPingPoingApp.sh`

---

## **How to interact with the PingPong App**

### **Sending a message**

You can send pings using the 2 libraries currently supported by the PingPong App.

1. Using the **Rukh Library** run the following command and follow the prompts

   `make send-rukh-ping`

2. Using the **Thunderbird Library** run the following command and follow the prompts

   `make send-thunderbird-ping`

---

## Don't Have Testnet tokens to send messages?

There are open source faucets you can find online. [Visit Alchemy](https://www.alchemy.com/best/crypto-faucets) to easily find a faucet.

If you are still having trouble finding tokens for using the PingPong App, ping us in the [discord group](https://discord.com/invite/7jETqRMBRc).
